START

1. Display Login Page

2. User enters Username and Password

3. IF login is valid THEN
       Open Dashboard
   ELSE
       Show "Invalid Login"
       Go to Login Page
   ENDIF

4. Display Menu:
       1. Student Management
       2. Lab Management
       3. Attendance
       4. System Status
       5. Reports
       6. Logout

5. User selects option

6. IF option = Student Management THEN
       Add / Update / Delete student details

7. ELSE IF option = Lab Management THEN
       Add / Update lab details
       View available systems

8. ELSE IF option = Attendance THEN
       Mark student attendance
       Save attendance record

9. ELSE IF option = System Status THEN
       View working / damaged systems

10. ELSE IF option = Reports THEN
        Generate attendance or lab usage report

11. ELSE IF option = Logout THEN
        Exit system

12. Repeat menu until Logout selected

STOP
